**This is a MULTI-REPO WORKSPACE, not a single project.** The repos below are cloned as subdirectories. Each repo has its own CLAUDE.md with repo-specific build commands, test runners, and lint configs. This file contains ONLY cross-repo context: relationships, codenames, deploy order, and tribal knowledge. Do not add repo-specific information here.

The repo registry is in `repos.json`. Run `make setup` to clone all repos.

> **Five highest-impact things to add to this file:**
> 1. System codenames — internal names Claude can't google
> 2. Cross-repo relationships — which service calls which, deploy order
> 3. Gotchas — things that have burned your team (include ticket numbers)
> 4. Non-obvious defaults — things that look standard but aren't
> 5. Repo map descriptions — expand the auto-generated one-liners below
>
> **Maintenance heuristic:** If you deleted a line and Claude would break something in the next 10 sessions, keep it. If Claude could figure it out from the code in 5 minutes, delete it. Update this file whenever Claude gets something wrong.

