## Safety Defaults

Never run destructive commands without explicit approval.

## Git Workflow

- Never push or merge directly to `main` — always use a branch and open a PR
- Only add relevant files (never use `git add -A` or `git add .`)
- Include tracker ticket as [__TRACKER_PREFIX__-1234] in commit messages
- Every commit must compile and pass tests

